---
/**
 * Redesigned Kind Words Section (Testimonials)
 */
---

<section class="testimonials section-pad">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="testimonials-header reveal">
            <h2>Kind Words</h2>
            <div class="accent-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
                <p>
                    I used to carry so much tension — emotionally and
                    physically. I felt full and cluttered. Through meditation
                    with Kari, I've cleared so much. I feel spacious, grounded,
                    and excited about the future instead of overwhelmed. I
                    didn't realise I could feel this calm.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
                <p>
                    I was rushed and scattered, constantly in my head. Now I
                    look forward to meditation every day — it's becoming a habit
                    I love. I feel calmer, clearer, and inspired to keep going.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
                <p>
                    I was exhausted from holding everything together — work,
                    family, life. Learning Vedic Meditation with Kari gave me
                    space to breathe again. I'm present, steady, and I finally
                    feel like myself.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card reveal">
                <p>
                    I want to let you know how grateful I am for our weekly
                    catch-ups. I get so much out of the mentoring and the
                    meditation. And the bonus — I am having the best sleep ever.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .testimonials {
        background: var(--color-indigo);
        color: var(--color-warm-white);
    }
    .testimonials-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 80px;
    }
    .testimonials-header h2 {
        font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px);
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--color-warm-white);
    }
    .testimonials-header .accent-line {
        background: var(--color-eucalyptus);
    }
    .testimonial-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 48px;
    }
    .testimonial-card {
        padding: 40px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(244, 242, 238, 0.08);
        background: rgba(244, 242, 238, 0.03);
        position: relative;
    }
    .testimonial-card::before {
        content: "“";
        position: absolute;
        top: 20px;
        left: 28px;
        font-family: var(--font-serif);
        font-size: 60px;
        color: var(--color-sea-green);
        opacity: 0.4;
        line-height: 1;
    }
    .testimonial-card p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: rgba(244, 242, 238, 0.8);
        font-style: italic;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .testimonial-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
